description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

 

This week, Kate and Leisha are answering questions about starting your career, Kate’s experience narrating an audiobook, how to get a foot in the door, and how they solve carpentry problems.

 

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram @ThePantsPod
